gitm.sh

small bash script to

o make bare repository on a remote host                         (-n)
o add it as a remote origin                                     (-n)
o adds local commit hook to push to origin                      (-n or -l)
o add hook on remote to send xmpp (TODO: configurabe user@host) (-n)
o (optional -- can be run at any time)                          (-g or -G)
     - create github repo                                       (-g)
     - add github remote origin to bare repo                    (-g or -G)
     - add hook on bare to push to github                       (-g or -G)
